{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to note that the suggestions do not constitute empirical evidence of what should change, but rather teacher perceptions.",
    "These changes to teaching are quite different from themes identified in previous reviews of AI in Education (e.g.",
    "Chiu et al., 2023b; Zhai et al., 2021).",
    "These educational possibilities do accord with some of the more innovative approaches suggested in emerging work from teachers (e.g.",
    "Kim et al., 2022), and highlight the range of new opportunities for teaching that generative AI avails."
  ]
}